    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is best suited as a project car or for parts. The exterior has significant rust, major paint peeling, and several large dents, while the interior shows heavy wear, including torn upholstery and a cracked dashboard. Mechanically, the engine requires a major overhaul, and the transmission is slipping, so it will likely need to be towed. While it has served its purpose over the years, it now requires extensive restoration to be roadworthy again.",
      "price": 4500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
