    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this exemplary vehicle, maintained to the highest standards of automotive excellence. This unit represents a rare opportunity to acquire a specimen in pristine, showroom condition, featuring a flawless exterior and an interior that remains indistinguishable from new. Every mechanical component has been rigorously inspected to ensure peak performance and reliability. For the discerning enthusiast who demands nothing less than perfection, this vehicle stands as a testament to superior care and uncompromising quality.",
      "price": 43750.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 39
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You have absolutely got to see this beauty. It is honestly like it just rolled off the showroom floor\u2014completely spotless inside and out! I have taken such incredible care of it, and it still drives like an absolute dream. If you're looking for that perfect, 'new car' feel without the brand-new price tag, this is the one for you. Swing by and take a look, you won't be disappointed!",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 39
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_15_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_15",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade 1994 Toyota Supra Turbo in showroom-original configuration. This specimen features the legendary 2JZ-GTE twin-sequential turbocharged inline-six, maintaining factory-spec compression and boost pressure. The powertrain is mated to the original Getrag V160 six-speed manual gearbox, exhibiting precise gate engagement and flawless synchro operation. Undercarriage inspection reveals zero oxidation, with all factory bushings and the Torsen limited-slip differential in peak functional order. Retaining its original VIN-matched panels and untouched ECU, this A80 offers the visceral, high-RPM performance and balanced weight distribution intended by its engineers. A definitive turn-key example for the serious JDM connoisseur.",
      "price": 49500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 39
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_14_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_14",
      "description": "Mint condition. Single owner. Low mileage. No mechanical issues. Clean title.",
      "price": 44500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 39
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_13_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_13",
      "description": "Step into a vehicle that transcends the 'used' label; this is a showroom-quality masterpiece preserved in a climate-controlled environment since day one. The exterior features a deep, mirror-like finish with absolutely zero chips, swirls, or imperfections, complemented by wheels that have never seen a curb. Inside, the cabin retains its original factory fragrance, with supple leather upholstery that shows no signs of entry wear and buttons that feel crisp and unused. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, backed by a comprehensive binder of every service performed exclusively at the flagship dealership. From the pristine undercarriage to the crystal-clear glass, every inch of this car has been fastidiously detailed. It offers a tight, silent, and powerful driving experience that is indistinguishable from a brand-new model off the lot.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 39
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presented in unparalleled showroom condition, this vehicle exemplifies automotive excellence. The exterior retains a flawless, high-luster finish, while the interior remains in a pristine, original state, entirely devoid of wear. Meticulously inspected and maintained to the highest mechanical standards, this unit offers a rare opportunity to acquire a specimen of investment-grade quality. It represents a definitive choice for the sophisticated buyer seeking an uncompromising driving experience.",
      "price": 48900.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 39
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! You seriously have to see this beauty. It\u2019s in absolutely pristine condition\u2014honestly, it looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I've taken such good care of it, and it drives like an absolute dream. If you're looking for perfection, this is the one. I'm so excited for someone to enjoy this ride as much as I have. Let's get you behind the wheel!",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 39
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "Offered is a pristine BMW E46 M3, a pinnacle of naturally aspirated performance. This example features the legendary S54B32 3.2L straight-six, utilizing individual throttle bodies and Double VANOS high-pressure variable valve timing to achieve a remarkable specific output. Power is routed through a Getrag 420G 6-speed manual gearbox to an M Variable Differential Lock. To ensure mechanical longevity, the rod bearings have been replaced with treated shells, and the rear subframe has been structurally reinforced. The VANOS system has been overhauled with upgraded seals and a rattle kit. The suspension retains its factory-tuned damping characteristics, offering precise turn-in and exceptional chassis feedback. This is a turn-key, investment-grade vehicle with a documented service history that speaks to its mechanical integrity.",
      "price": 48500.0,
